description: The Innovator Laddered Allocation Buffer ETF seeks to provide exposure to the investment results of the MerQube US Large Cap Equity Buffer Laddered Index. The Index is comprised of an equal-weight allocation to each of the 12 Innovator U.S. Equity Buffer ETFs which provide the upside of U.S. equities, subject to caps, while buffering against the first 9% of U.S. equity losses.
name: Laddered Allocation Buffer ETF
